dcterms:description: The MICCAI 2015 Head and Neck Auto Segmentation Challenge dataset consists of CT images with organ annotations, used for evaluating segmentation methods in head and neck imaging.

dcterms:description: A self-collected HaN dataset consisting of 50 CT scans with manual annotations of 18 organs by doctors, used for training and testing segmentation methods.
dcterms:title: Self-collected HaN dataset
